 Data Blending | Domo 





































Blend your data into one digestible story.  




Watch demo














You’ve got data here, there, and everywhere. And let’s face it: Without a way to combine all of this data into a single view, it’s hard to know what impact any of it has on your business—or your bottom line.
With Domo, you can join, combine, analyze, and govern data from any source in one intuitive platform. When you can measure metrics against each other, you can start to unveil new patterns or trends in your data—and start making better, smarter, and more strategic business decisions.


Connect to any source of data: With Domo, you can quickly and easily connect to any source of data to no matter what it is or where it lives.
Simplify closed-loop reporting:  Combine analytics with sales, marketing, and finance data to effectively measure success.
Make new connections:  Easily blend data sources to discover new relationships in your data and see the bigger picture.

 
