About APD
American Product Distributors, Inc. (APD) combines consulting, information technology and product distribution to deliver custom solutions to large enterprises.  We provide the information needed to make better business decisions and the automated controls needed to ensure execution of those decisions, resulting in cost savings and a more streamlined procurement process.  APD creates custom electronic catalogs for office supplies, industrial/MRO products, corporate identity products and other product categories as requested.
Key Facts:
•            Founded in 1992•            Number of users serviced - over 100,000•             Number of customer locations - over 400,000•            Number of orders processed annually - 300,000•            Number of catalogs managed - nearly 200
       APD Warehouse Locations






Nationwide distribution network of 31 warehouses 
Access to 9 million square feet of storage
Over 40,000 skus available for next-day delivery









 































 

