eLink™ is a custom built on-line procurement catalog system incorporating every vendor selling to your organization.  APD will “load” each vendor’s purchasing catalog or product listing to this on-line system for maximum order efficiency, cost control and accountability.  APD will build, install and maintain the on-line system with a shared cost arrangement with your vendors.
Major Benefits for Buying Organizations

  Synchronized ordering process across all vendors
  Significant cost savings
  Automated on-line ordering across all vendors
  Absolute control of ordering at “point of purchase”
  Synchronized superior management reporting
  Supplier diversity utilization

eLink™ is a custom built on-line procurement catalog system for companies that want to sell their products to other organizations who expect or require eCatalog ordering.  APD will build, install and maintain the catalog at a nominal cost to you, our customer.
Major Benefits for Selling Organizations 

  Synchronized ordering process for B2B transactions
  Significant cost savings
  Automated on-line ordering across all customers
  Absolute control of ordering at “point of purchase”
  Synchronized superior management reporting
  Supplier diversity utilization


 



















