Value Innovation





JUST WHAT IS IT?
eLink™ is a customized automated program that systematically drives down procurement costs to achieve sustained, continuous cost savings year over year.
 
HOW WAS IT CREATED?
We used our in-depth knowledge and 20 plus years of experience in   supply chain operations, consulting and systems development to create   our unique strategy of systematically providing on-going cost savings to corporate customers.
 
WHAT IS THE BASIC COST SAVINGS STRATEGY?
Simply put, our system continuously drives down procurement costs by controlling product price while totally managing product CHOICE both at the company level and at the employee point of purchase.
 
WHAT DOES THIS SYSTEM DO? 
Gives Senior Procurement Management the ANALYTICAL INFORMATION to make major procurement cost savings decisions and the AUTOMATED CONTROLS needed to ensure the execution of those decisions.






 































 

