ScrumSoftware Development










We Build Custom Software For Any Platform


Our mission at Surge is to provide high-end software development & consulting services to our clients that are unmatched in the industry. Our expert onshore team will build your software solution up to 40% faster with 100% precision.

Everything Agile
After years of business, we know that plans often change. That’s why we’re passionate proponents of the Agile development method. Every project is given a road map, then broken down into “sprints” as we execute rapid delivery of your project one element at a time. This guarantees that every component is either done to your satisfaction or given modifications at your request. We’ve perfected the process of adaptation and collaboration between our teams and our clients, and the end result is a thing of beauty. 

100% Scrum Certified
At Surge, we require all of our Project Managers to be scrum certified in order to ensure the highest level of productivity, transparency, and success. Rest assured, your next project will be managed in an efficient and organized manner. This is just one of the ways we maximize your dollar and quicken your timeline.



Quality Code Matters
